<P>MAX. IV. The aperture being the same, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> effect will be nearly as the cube of the velocity of the water.</P>
<P>This also will appear by comparing the con|tents of columns 3, 8 and 10, as for
